<BaseLayout
  title="About - T-001v2r3"
  description="Learn more about me, my background, interests, and what I do."
>
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
          About Me
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Welcome! Let me introduce myself.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-dark">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            Hello, I'm T-001v2r3
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Welcome to my personal website! This is a space where I share my thoughts,
            experiences, and projects with the world.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            I'm passionate about technology, learning, and creating things that make a difference.
            This site serves as both a portfolio and a blog where I document my journey.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            What I Do
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            I work on various projects and share my learnings through blog posts. My interests include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li>Software development and engineering</li>
            <li>Web technologies and modern frameworks</li>
            <li>Open source contributions</li>
            <li>Continuous learning and self-improvement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            This Website
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            This site is built with modern technologies to provide a fast, accessible, and
            pleasant reading experience:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Astro</strong> - A modern static site generator</li>
            <li><strong>TypeScript</strong> - For type-safe code</li>
            <li><strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - For beautiful, responsive styling</li>
            <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> - For reliable hosting and deployment</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            The site features a dark/light theme toggle, RSS feed, and is fully responsive
            across all devices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            Get In Touch
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Feel free to explore my blog and read about my projects and experiences.
            You can also subscribe to my <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">RSS feed</a> to
